♪ Can you make me feel better? ♪

1292
01:19:09.041 --> 01:19:12.291
♪ This could be a good night
for good times ♪

1293
01:19:12.375 --> 01:19:15.083
♪ And you look like
a good time ♪

1294
01:19:15.166 --> 01:19:18.791
♪ We're dancing
to Dancing in the Moonlight ♪

1295
01:19:18.875 --> 01:19:21.250
♪ Now I want you bad ♪

1296
